<h3 id="principles">Principles<a class="self-link" href="#principles"></a></h3>
<p>The WHATWG is guided by <a href="principles">Principles</a> of openness, utility, efficiency, and freedom.</p>
<h3 id="policies">Policies<a class="self-link" href="#policies"></a></h3>
<p>WHATWG participants operate under a number of policies:</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="ipr-policy">Intellectual Property Rights Policy</a></li>
<li><a href="workstream-policy">Workstream Policy</a></li>
<li><a href="code-of-conduct">Code of Conduct</a></li>
<li><a href="https://whatwg.org/working-mode">Working Mode</a></li>
</ul>
<p>Additionally, the WHATWG Steering Group was created by the <a href="sg-agreement">Steering Group Agreement</a> and operates under the <a href="sg-policy">Steering Group Policy</a>.</p>
